# MyMoolah Overview

MyMoolah is a banking-grade Treasury Platform for South Africa.

- Production: `api-mm.mymoolah.africa`, `wallet.mymoolah.africa`.
- Stack: Node.js/Express, PostgreSQL Cloud SQL, React/Vite, GCP Cloud Run/GCS/Secret Manager.
- Domains: wallet, double-entry ledger, VAS, KYC, USSD, PayShap/SBSA H2H, reconciliation, admin portal.
- Standards: Mojaloop-aligned, ISO 20022, POPIA, FICA-aware, banking-grade auditability.

